base_armor.property_description: The amount of armor points this entity has when not wearing anything else.

bucketable.property_description: Whether this entity can be picked up with waterbuckets.

can_be_ridden_in_water.property_description: Whether this entity can be ridden in water.

can_be_saddled.property_description: Whether this entity can be saddled.

can_breathe_in_water.property_description: Whether this entity can breathe when under water.

can_open_doors.property_description: Whether this entity can open doors.

can_pick_up_items.property_description: Whether this entity has the ability to pick up items that are beside it.

can_ride_boat.property_description: Whether this entity has the ability to mount boats.

can_ride_minecart.property_description: Whether this entity has the ability to mount minecarts.

fire_immune.property_description: Whether this entity is immune to fire damage.

height_offset.property_description: The height offset this entity adds to itself when riding a vehicle.

hurt_by_water.property_description: Whether this entity is hurt by water, rain and splash/lingering water bottles.

leadable.property_description: Whether this entity can be leashed with leads.

living.property_description:
Whether this entity is living or not. 
This includes armor stands.

max_health.property_description: The max health of this entity.

entries.Drowned: 20.0 and 40.0 - 100.0 (Spawns with 20.0 health due to MC-219981)
entries.Husk: 20.0 and 40.0 - 100.0 (Spawns with 20.0 health due to MC-219981)
entries.Zombie: 20.0 and 40.0 - 100.0 (Spawns with 20.0 health due to MC-219981)
entries.Zombie Villager: 20.0 and 40.0 - 100.0 (Spawns with 20.0 health due to MC-219981)
entries.Zombified Piglin: 20.0 and 40.0 - 100.0 (Spawns with 20.0 health due to MC-219981)

mob_category.property_description: Determines what mob cap this entity uses when spawning.

mounted_height_offset.property_description: The height offset this entity adds to its passengers.

persistency.property_description: Whether this entity is persistent or can despawn.

entries.Arrow: Will despawn after one minute of not moving
entries.Cod: Can despawn unless they were bucketed once
entries.Evoker: Can despawn unless part of a raid or spawned in with a woodland mansion
entries.Hoglin: Can despawn unless spawned in with bastions or are bred
entries.Piglin: Can despawn unless spawned in with bastions
entries.Pufferfish: Can despawn unless they were bucketed once
entries.Salmon: Can despawn unless they were bucketed once
entries.Skeleton: Can despawn unless spawned in with skeleton traps during thunderstorms
entries.Thrown Ender Pearl: Can despawn if the owner dies when the pearl is loaded
entries.Tropical Fish: Can despawn unless they were bucketed once
entries.Vindicator: Can despawn unless part of a raid or spawned in with a woodland mansion
entries.Warden: Can despawn after one minute of not being angered
entries.Witch: Can despawn unless spawned in with witch huts or converted from villagers with lightning
entries.Wolf: Can despawn if angered and untamed
entries.Zombified Piglin: Can despawn unless they were converted from pigs with lightning

saved_on_reload.property_description:
Whether this entity is saved to the world. 
Entities that are not saved are lost when unloaded.

shearable.property_description: Whether this entity can be sheared

spawns_inside_hazards.property_description:
Normally dangerous blocks that this entity can spawn inside.
This only includes wither roses, sweet berry bushes, and powder snow.
See Fire Immune for entities that can spawn inside of fire.

xp_dropped.property_description:
The amount of experience points this entity drops upon its death.
Note that the mobs do not drop experience orbs unless it dies within five seconds (100 game ticks) of an attack registered as a player hit.
